6772fa5ef577e5a1c3ee55e29d4e197fd5","tid":442352,"uid":53836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T14:25:50.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦, 個人覺得輔導員反而幫助唔大<br />\n<br />\n我都係抑鬱咗好長一段時間, 無咩特別事發生都會無啦啦非常非常唔開心. <br />\n不過前排睇醫生, 開咗隻藥比我, 真係超有效, 已經唔會再無啦啦好想死, 先記得翻原來無抑鬱係咁幸福ge事！<br />\n<br />\n真心, 快睇, 好快無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8a6e9cb39a85e53c028f9c22314137fa58329a","tid":442352,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:08:51.000Z","msg":"改變唔到現況其實睇醫生都冇用"},{"pid":"50ca169dc020837260a4cdb59b8af8858d46004e","tid":442352,"uid":126831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:32:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>改變唔到現況其實睇醫生都冇用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抑鬱可能因為冇左某d cell，要食藥先得。"},{"pid":"654345c9f807f52c1a361d05087eb8254e015d42","tid":442352,"uid":89206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉我都係咁，自從女朋友突然分手之後就有哂啲症狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓唔到食唔到野，做咩都冇哂動力，仲諗過死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但冇錢去睇私家，到最後過左兩個月而家叫做好返少少，但情緒都係keep住低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴找我係過來人，有輕度抑鬱，有睇醫生<br />\n都係啱分手，想同你講睇醫生無用，因為佢只會不停叫你分散注意，但其實解鈴還需繫鈴人。<br />\n<br />\n藥物只係控制，但改不變心態。我都仲著緊佢，所以一路鬱鬱寡歡，一個人好易失神亂諗同注意唔到周圍嘅野，成日會好失落，然後乜都唔學持續一段時間"},{"pid":"61ee9b8cf6fb715bf6d4a91b76e8c7f2c9f3b033","tid":442352,"uid":116780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"有想死諗頭。番工集中 唔到 諗唔到生存為咩 唔想食野 唔想郁 死啦 7年無出現 係咪又復發"},{"pid":"c882a6376ba03a4117e017935a446a311fa7eb88","tid":442352,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有想死諗頭。番工集中 唔到 諗唔到生存為咩 唔想食野 唔想郁 死啦 7年無出現 係咪又復發</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無信仰？"},{"pid":"7f1abb8f545b52e626d9ec936619664fbd2b3623","tid":442352,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:39:50.000Z","msg":"唉 呢個月好想放負"},{"pid":"562d0a6b0a7b75ae2453d2a845be59faed68abd6","tid":442352,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過因為唔主動開topic同俾唔到屎<br />\n仲有少搵人比人嬲鳩"},{"pid":"5f048f000cdc357a26f0b392bf749523a34de270","tid":442352,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:43:16.000Z","msg":"學校<br />\n家庭<br />\n人際<br />\n風火倫咁接住煩<br />\n<br />\n屋企單親 而家要撐起頭家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb203360e334d68d944e11400568d52319ca0a0e","tid":442352,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>OP 你不如試下講下你認為有啲咩做得唔好？<br />\n相信你只感到抑鬱而唔係真正抑鬱</blockquote><br />\n樣樣野煩完一樣又煩一樣"},{"pid":"54e56f7e9cf0e339c7b31ca8089f5769c5e88a83","tid":442352,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2766404c4c0ae59496e580922034aace5a4d48e","tid":442352,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f8c24c003cf724ebd36a968dbc184fa15aefc91d","tid":442352,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:12:11.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f7c2c27b4dbf922ebf5b8af00e71164ff0636c5a","tid":442352,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:21:00.000Z","msg":"邊到有得搵社工/心理輔導員傾吓"},{"pid":"0b6cda9e40469f23fa0c09abd2baa3e3fe2d0e83","tid":442352,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:49:18